          卓越产品
        </h1>
        <p id="hero-subtitle" class="text-[clamp(1.1rem,2vw,1.5rem)] text-white/90 hero-fade max-w-2xl mx-auto">面向工业和商业应用的先进电能质量解决方案。</p>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-[clamp(8px,1.5vw,20px)] mt-8 opacity-0 animate-[decorIn_0.8s_0.6s_ease_forwards]">
